<P>
FIRE KILLS FOUR IN FAMILY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By UPI 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
CHARLOTTE, N. C. 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Four members of a family died and two others were critically injured when a 
fire swept through their small house, authorities said. They said the fire 
Sunday was believed to have started by a smoldering cigarette. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
